product.title: Tweet Tweet Bubble Chick Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Meet Tweet Tweet, the newest member of the Bubble Chick family!

    Who says chickens can't be cute and stylish? Tweet Tweet Bubble Chick Hoodie has a fun and playful design, perfect for your little one to strut her stuff. With a charming little chick print and an adorable hood designed to hold up all of those ruffled feathers, this sweatshirt is certain to make your pet feel super special.

    Choose between 12 different colors, suitable for both men and women. We always recommend choosing 1 size up giving you the oversized hoodie look.




    Get ready to give your look a kawaii-style with this oversized hoodie!

    Unique and stylish design that will make you look super cute. Made from premium quality polyester, this hoodie is like no other and feels soft and smooth on the skin. A super comfortable overlay for everyday wear.

    Available in five different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below. 

    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 41 43 44 46 48
    Length 23 24 25 26 27
    Sleeve 20 20 20 21 21
               
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 106 110 114 118 122
    Length 60 62 64 66 68
    Sleeve 50 51 52 53 54


    Features

    😍 Made from 70% premium polyester and 30% pure cotton
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.


  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
